      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i'm just in everyone's way lately. my joints hurt so much and i can't even make tea without help anymore. my kids are so busy with their own lives, and i can see them struggling every time they come over to help me with stuff. i just feel like such a weight on them.",
